    "modelData": {
        "filePath": "examples/SimpleLoop.graph",
        "fileType": "Graph",
        "shortDescription": "Graph using actual data and the Branch App.",
        "detailedDescription": "The graph is generating an array of random numbers and decides whether to continue the loop in one branch or the other, depending on whether the currently picked value of the array is smaller than a certain value. Other than  the LoopWithExit graph this loop will always run  till the end and only skip a few internal drops.",
